# MYUA

## Example

### Basic

```html
<amp-embed
  width="300"
  height="400"
  type="myua"
  data-sid="1"
  data-iid="1"
>
</amp-embed>
```

## Configuration

For details on the configuration semantics, please contact the ad network or refer to their documentation.

### Required parameters

-   `data-sid`
-   `data-iid`

### Optional parameters

-   `data-env`
-   `data-options`
